data.description: Updated open concept living! Make this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom house your NextHome! Main floor features open, spacious kitchen with great counter space, dining area big enough to fit a large table and living room with large picture window full of sunlight.  Three bedrooms all on the main level with full bathroom. Basement is finished with full bathroom and laundry.  All appliances are included.  Two car garage is heated with back ally entrance.  Schedule a showing today!
